# Final check for connectivity and density:
# - All Resources are locatedAtLocus and have resourceManagedBy.
# - All NetworkInterfaces are networkInterfaceOf a Resource and networkInterfaceConnects a NetworkLink.
# - All NetworkLinks have termination resources.
# - All ApplicationModules are applicationModuleOf an Application and have a managedBy agent.
# - All Services are composed of ApplicationModules/Resources.
# - All TroubleTickets are related to Services/Applications/Resources and Agents, and have trigger events.
# - All ChangeRequests are related to Resources/Applications/Services and Agents.
# - All EventRecords originate from Resources/Applications/Agents and are linked to TroubleTickets/ChangeRequests.
# - All KOS concepts are used.
# - All core NORIA classes and properties are used multiple times.
# - No ldp prefix.
# - Labels and comments are present.
# - Dates and other literal values are varied.
# - The graph is structured logically.
